 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_InstantBitmap_Inputs|
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_InstantBitmap_Inputs|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_InstantBitmap_Input1|
